      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": " On May 5, 1952, [REDACTED] called at this",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Bureau and advised that he is General Manager of [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Netherlands.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "He resides at [REDACTED] He is residing",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "at the Victoria Hotel, New York City, until May 16, 1952,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "when he will return to Europe.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": " Mr. [REDACTED] advised that he has a considerable",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "interest in electronics and has been very much interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "in reports circulated during the past year or two concern-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "ing the existence of flying saucers. He feels that there",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "have been enough uncontradicted reports concerning such",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "devices to indicate that they may exist in fact. He is also",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "of the opinion that if they do exist they can be produced",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "only by the United States or Russia or perhaps by the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Republic of Argentina.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": " Mr. [REDACTED] indicated that he has given extensive",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "thought to the manner in which these devices could be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "operated. He has concluded that since the disk shape is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "not suitable for conventional aircraft it would be used",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "only because it would provide the greatest possible lifting",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "surface. It is his opinion, therefore, that one of these",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "devices could be operated only by reducing the air pressure",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "above it which would cause it to rise in the air. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "concedes that conventional machinery to cause such a reduction",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "of pressure would be so bulky that its weight would prevent",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "the device from leaving the ground. He concludes, therefore,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
